      "text": [
        " لَهُ عَلِيٌّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ \"زِدْهَا فَإِنَّهُ أَعْظَمُ لِلْبَرَكَةِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3736 - Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) passed by a bondwoman who had bought meat from a butcher and was asking him to add more.\nImam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said to the butcher: \"Give her more, for it brings greater blessings.\""
        ]
      }
